{"type": "article", "id": 10960, "title": "OP vase 万花筒花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-18T07:28:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052359463kedQwDTyqMEUCJN.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">土耳其设计师</span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"> Bilge Nur Saltik </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">的作品 </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">OP 系列</span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">花瓶首次在 </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">2015 </span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">年米兰设计周上亮相，设计师想要通过外部玻璃罩的扭转来呈现花束的另一种视觉效果，利用万花筒原理，从每个角度看都会有不同的视觉感受，从一朵花变幻出千万朵。每个玻璃外罩都是手工吹制，全系列有三种尺寸，并且各自有不同颜色和切口设计，组合起来也是一道缤纷风景。售价 350 美元，</span><a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/op-vase-kaleidoscopic-bilge-nur-saltik-04-23-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a><span style=\"text-align:left;\">。\r\n\t<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235943TwpVy4a70ZP1DUJ6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235944xUSF8tr52qKeXdRa.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235944k3P5vhbF81nsTior.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235944zingB703MfNj8m9r.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235945uX8QfPJw4N65dYr9.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t